Advent International Mulls Investment in All Saints, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-10T19:40:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/advent-international-mulls-investment-in-all-saints-sky-says.html
Advent International is considering
investing in U.K. clothing retailer All Saints and may submit
its proposal to Ernst & Young LLP, which is handling the
process, tomorrow, Sky News City Editor Mark Kleinman  reported 
in his blog on the website without attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
